WEBVTT

00:00:00.632 --> 00:00:03.816
-ET NUMERO TRES, VIDEO CASSETTE

00:00:04.125 --> 00:00:06.122
FAJWEL ZYLBERBERG

00:00:06.150 --> 00:00:09.202
fey, tsvey yudn, tsvey vovn, lamed

00:00:09.202 --> 00:00:12.652
zayen yud lamed beys ayen reysh

00:00:12.652 --> 00:00:14.767
beys ayen reysh giml.

00:00:14.925 --> 00:00:19.223
mayn nomen iz Elyohu Toker, alef lamed yud hey vov

00:00:19.363 --> 00:00:21.934
tes alef kuf ayen reysh

00:00:21.934 --> 00:00:26.044
s'iz der draysikster may, toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsik

00:00:26.044 --> 00:00:29.164
in BUENOS AIRES Argentine oyf yidish.

00:00:29.943 --> 00:00:31.524
 Fayvl.

00:00:31.243 --> 00:00:31.980
yo?

00:00:32.120 --> 00:00:38.780
 ir hot gezogt az s'iz aroys nor a por shures in PRAVDA vegn dem

00:00:38.887 --> 00:00:40.513
 Varshever geto.

00:00:39.039 --> 00:00:40.518
vegn ⟨-shav-⟩ geto.

00:00:40.558 --> 00:00:42.172
 ir hot es geleyent?

00:00:41.705 --> 00:00:42.386
yo.

00:00:42.386 --> 00:00:43.674
ikh hob es geleyent.

00:00:44.473 --> 00:00:46.222
es hot tsirkulirt.

00:00:46.059 --> 00:00:48.146
vos hot ir farshtanen derfun?

00:00:47.645 --> 00:00:49.026
ikh hob farshtanen

00:00:49.026 --> 00:00:50.166
az der bagrif

00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:52.719
a spetsyeln voyn batsirk vil zogn geto

00:00:53.872 --> 00:00:55.284
vil zogn der geto.

00:00:55.695 --> 00:00:57.613
ober keyn shum yedies

00:00:58.361 --> 00:01:00.937
vegn dem vos kumt for faktish

00:01:02.411 --> 00:01:06.101
oyf di okupirte, in Poyln, in Poyln unter di Natsi hershaft

00:01:06.275 --> 00:01:07.884
hot men nisht gevust

00:01:07.884 --> 00:01:10.928
az yene tsayt hot eksistirt nokh di groyse libe

00:01:11.203 --> 00:01:13.104
tsvishn Stalin un Hitler.

00:01:13.987 --> 00:01:15.129
faktish

00:01:15.303 --> 00:01:16.929
iz

00:01:16.929 --> 00:01:19.500
sovyet Rusland geven di tsushtelerin

00:01:20.028 --> 00:01:21.305
fun veyts

00:01:21.564 --> 00:01:22.557
petrol

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:24.377
un koyln far Daytshland.

00:01:26.340 --> 00:01:27.803
oyf azoy vayt

00:01:28.736 --> 00:01:30.857
az ikh hob gearbet in Zdolbunev

00:01:31.402 --> 00:01:33.506
gevoynt hot men in vagonen

00:01:33.731 --> 00:01:35.447
lebn di ban stantsye.

00:01:36.887 --> 00:01:38.755
a umgehoyere tsol

00:01:39.502 --> 00:01:40.728
fleg dokh zeen.

00:01:42.118 --> 00:01:45.201
eshalonen, komplet eshalonen fun kol tuv

00:01:45.712 --> 00:01:46.803
iz gegangen

00:01:46.860 --> 00:01:49.031
tsu di grenets, alts keyn Daytshland.

00:01:50.437 --> 00:01:53.975
m'hot zikh afile nisht forgeshtelt az s'ken kumen tsu dem

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:55.899
⟨far⟩

00:01:57.305 --> 00:02:00.793
in merts UNK farlozt di militerishe UNK

00:02:01.338 --> 00:02:03.880
merts april, s'heyst zogn peysekh tsayt

00:02:04.224 --> 00:02:05.383
kumt for

00:02:05.642 --> 00:02:08.606
dos shikn di rekrutn in militer.

00:02:09.236 --> 00:02:11.542
⟨iz⟩ nokh geforn gants eshalonen

00:02:14.923 --> 00:02:18.565
mit yunge rekrutn, akhtsn yor, nayntsn yor, azoy vi UNK

00:02:18.565 --> 00:02:20.649
on shum militerishe aynibung

00:02:20.576 --> 00:02:21.853
di rusishe

00:02:20.649 --> 00:02:22.725
geganen tsu di grenets.

00:02:21.909 --> 00:02:23.051
rusishe.

00:02:22.725 --> 00:02:23.659
rusishe.

00:02:24.288 --> 00:02:25.497
rusishe UNK.

00:02:25.622 --> 00:02:29.678
in Ratnfarband iz nisht bloyz Rusland; Ratnfarband UNK tsendliker UNK

00:02:29.678 --> 00:02:31.101
natsyonalitetn.

00:02:31.170 --> 00:02:32.399
iz vos iz

00:02:31.393 --> 00:02:33.829
iz alts geganen tsu di grenets.

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:35.691
ver hot zikh gekent forshteln

00:02:36.270 --> 00:02:38.019
az in dray monat arum

00:02:38.126 --> 00:02:39.555
vet oysbrekhn

00:02:41.484 --> 00:02:43.352
aza shoyderlekher krig

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:45.006
vos me shikt zelner

00:02:45.348 --> 00:02:47.789
on shum aynibungen tsu di grenets?

00:02:48.453 --> 00:02:52.835
iz ven iz oysgebrokhn- ven s'iz oysgebrokhn der

00:02:52.065 --> 00:02:55.637
dos iz oysgebrokhn in eyn un tsvontsikstn yuni

00:02:55.895 --> 00:02:56.863
eyn un tsvan-

00:02:56.863 --> 00:02:57.563
eyn ts-

00:02:57.563 --> 00:02:58.337
tsvey

00:02:58.933 --> 00:02:59.754
yuni

00:02:59.979 --> 00:03:01.728
in eyn un fertsikstn yor

00:03:01.532 --> 00:03:04.749
in eyn un fertsikstn yor iz di ershte onfli

00:03:05.025 --> 00:03:06.690
fun daytshe avyonen

00:03:06.948 --> 00:03:09.389
⟨hobn mir⟩ geshtanen un gekukt, ⟨dakht zikh⟩ undzere.

00:03:09.733 --> 00:03:12.124
s'iz manevres, biz m'hot zikh gekhapt

00:03:14.643 --> 00:03:16.949
az Daytshland iz ibergefaln.

00:03:17.327 --> 00:03:20.443
er hot ongehoybn di milkhome kegn Rusland.

00:03:22.676 --> 00:03:26.670
di grupe, vos mir hobn gevoynt in di vagones, gearbet bay di ayznbanen

00:03:28.228 --> 00:03:30.450
hot men fun undz gemakht, azoy tsu zogn

00:03:31.265 --> 00:03:33.352
a grupe fun ⟨ayznbanen⟩

00:03:35.535 --> 00:03:41.064
un mit, tsvey vagon, a vagon ⟨tsu shterner⟩, un a vagon mit shpaln, mit shines

00:03:41.627 --> 00:03:45.401
vi di daytshn hobn bombardirt dem veg, flegn mir tsuforn un farrekhtn.

00:03:47.010 --> 00:03:49.401
farleygn frishe shpaln, firshe shines.

00:03:49.912 --> 00:03:52.289
iz undzer UNK geven fun

00:03:52.325 --> 00:03:53.568
Zdolbunev

00:03:53.642 --> 00:03:54.801
biz Rovne.

00:03:56.510 --> 00:03:58.414
fun Zdolbunev iz avekgeganen der veg

00:03:58.414 --> 00:04:01.874
di ayznban veg arop oyf dorem un oyf mizrekh

00:04:01.874 --> 00:04:03.694
nokh Shepetovke keyn Kiev.

00:04:05.741 --> 00:04:06.562
nu?

00:04:07.665 --> 00:04:09.161
iz vos iz geshen?

00:04:07.682 --> 00:04:09.077
un

00:04:10.010 --> 00:04:11.658
vos iz geshen vayter?

00:04:10.348 --> 00:04:15.000
forn azoy hin un tsurik, biz Rovne vert bombardirt durkh di avyonen

00:04:15.191 --> 00:04:18.965
oyf a shoyderlekhn ⟨oyfn⟩, dos ershte vos vert tseklapt un tsezetst

00:04:19.545 --> 00:04:21.921
un di ban ⟨di relsn⟩, di ban stantsye

00:04:21.921 --> 00:04:22.813
in Rovne.

00:04:24.084 --> 00:04:26.897
un s'hot zikh ongehoybn der tsuriktsi

00:04:27.543 --> 00:04:29.056
fun der royter armey

00:04:29.838 --> 00:04:31.844
un m'hot zikh bamit vos mer

00:04:31.844 --> 00:04:34.052
vos me ken ⟨oyf⟩ mer aroysfirn

00:04:34.665 --> 00:04:37.106
geven gantse eshalonen mit farvundete.

00:04:40.402 --> 00:04:44.126
dos iz geven in di fri. me arbetn op, mir arbetn op

00:04:44.300 --> 00:04:48.513
in a sho arum, in tsvey, kumen di daytshn bombardirn vider di zelbe linye.

00:04:50.139 --> 00:04:51.062
iz geven

00:04:51.759 --> 00:04:53.250
a groyse ⟨shpyonazh⟩.

00:04:53.250 --> 00:04:54.437
oder

00:04:56.636 --> 00:05:00.883
der iker iz az, akht a zeyger bay di nakht shoyn far der nakht

00:05:02.627 --> 00:05:06.688
hot shoyn di daytshe armey ongehoybn tsu bombardirn Rovne

00:05:07.436 --> 00:05:09.135
mit artilerye.

00:05:10.608 --> 00:05:14.096
un azoy vi mir zenen nisht geven mundirt, in tsivil

00:05:15.114 --> 00:05:17.521
iz dokh di gantse grupe funandergefaln

00:05:18.540 --> 00:05:21.836
azoy UNK bombardirt shoyn Rovne mit artilerye

00:05:21.864 --> 00:05:24.170
vil zogn az di daytshn zenen shoyn noent.

00:05:26.555 --> 00:05:32.236
bin ikh in, shoyn fintster, iz UNK bin ikh gelofn fun Rovne biz Zdolbunev, dakht zikh ⟨bay⟩ yene

00:05:32.597 --> 00:05:35.443
yene moment geshlogn dem rekord fun loyfn.

00:05:36.697 --> 00:05:40.944
ober di gantse zakh iz nokh geven vos di ukraynishe natsyonalistn

00:05:41.422 --> 00:05:43.441
hobn ongehoybn tsu bashisn

00:05:44.662 --> 00:05:47.525
dos alts vos flegt zikh bavegn oyf di ban relsn.

00:05:49.505 --> 00:05:51.136
ongekumen keyn Zdolbunev

00:05:52.374 --> 00:05:57.228
fartog hob ikh gekhapt a valizke, arayngeleygt mayne por zakhn, gelofn tsu di ban stantsye

00:05:57.504 --> 00:05:58.916
un shoyn.

00:05:59.276 --> 00:06:04.907
faktish geven der letster eshalon, der letster tsug vos fl- iz aroysgeganen fun Zdolbunev.

00:06:06.009 --> 00:06:07.235
vu ahin?

00:06:07.128 --> 00:06:10.509
keyn, oyf Kiev, keyn Shepetovke. arayn keyn Rusland.

00:06:10.734 --> 00:06:15.808
⟨gezogt frier⟩ vos m'hot gekent aroysfirn, vos iz geven meglekh aroystsufirn mentshn materyal

00:06:15.999 --> 00:06:18.924
iz do materyal fun di ayznban iz alts avek

00:06:18.952 --> 00:06:20.010
oyf mizrekh.

00:06:22.327 --> 00:06:28.076
aroyfgeshprungen oyf di ban, fun shpringen, aroysshpringen fun banen iz shoyn nisht geven bay mir keyn nayes

00:06:29.837 --> 00:06:31.755
me kumt in mitn veg

00:06:32.891 --> 00:06:36.480
opgeshtelt di gantse ba- ayznban trafik. vos iz geshen?

00:06:36.654 --> 00:06:39.163
di daytshn hobn ⟨op⟩gehakt di telegrafn linyes

00:06:40.232 --> 00:06:41.863
zey hobn aroysgeshikt

00:06:42.577 --> 00:06:44.090
a falshn bafel

00:06:44.282 --> 00:06:46.622
az ⟨zey veln⟩ tsurikforn keyn Zdolbunev.

00:06:48.855 --> 00:06:51.381
s'iz geven naye rusishe

00:06:51.538 --> 00:06:56.848
lokomotiv mashinistn. eyn mashinist zogt az ⟨er⟩ tsurik fort nisht. er fort oyf Shepetovke.

00:06:57.714 --> 00:07:02.028
az ikh hob gehert az er fort UNK in zayn ban, dan ⟨eshalon iz⟩ geven der ershter.

00:07:02.844 --> 00:07:05.994
bin ikh im nokhgelofn, aroyfgeshprungen oyf di tsveyte ban

00:07:07.097 --> 00:07:09.589
un di ban heybt on avektsuforn

00:07:10.539 --> 00:07:12.997
zetst zikh arop a daytsher desant

00:07:13.593 --> 00:07:14.887
hinter undz.

00:07:16.918 --> 00:07:19.747
az der mashinist hot derzen dem daytshn desant

00:07:20.580 --> 00:07:22.329
hot er gegebn pare

00:07:23.820 --> 00:07:26.987
un arayngeforn in Shepetovke

00:07:27.448 --> 00:07:30.041
mit di greste shnelkeyt vos ⟨iz nor⟩ meglekh geven.

00:07:30.857 --> 00:07:33.281
fun Shepetovke iz arayn keyn Kiev.

00:07:34.383 --> 00:07:38.427
ongekumen keyn Kiev, UNK nokh geven a shtikl ordenung, far

00:07:39.463 --> 00:07:42.194
di rusishe royter kreyts iz aroysgekumen

00:07:42.213 --> 00:07:43.490
mit broyt

00:07:43.715 --> 00:07:45.751
mit tey tsu di vagonen.

00:07:46.905 --> 00:07:49.920
az ⟨shoyn denstmol⟩ geven a groyse behole.

00:07:51.883 --> 00:07:53.767
fun dort, fun Kiev

00:07:54.735 --> 00:07:58.993
hob ikh iber⟨UNK⟩ gekhapt a tsveyte ban, un alts di mase vagonen

00:07:58.993 --> 00:08:02.121
alts vagonen, un vagonen, leydike vagonen

00:08:03.155 --> 00:08:05.343
oyf avektsufirn tif keyn Rusland

00:08:07.627 --> 00:08:09.393
bin ikh shoyn mit di ban

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:11.773
ongekumen keyn KUIBYSHEV.

00:08:12.487 --> 00:08:14.776
nokh tsvey nekht un dray teg forn.

00:08:15.812 --> 00:08:21.274
eyn tog iz men shoyn nisht farbrent gevorn far hits, far di ban hot zikh nisht opgeshtelt in ergets.

00:08:21.954 --> 00:08:25.172
vi lang hot gegat vaser un koyln hot er zikh nisht opgeshtelt.

00:08:26.578 --> 00:08:28.969
⟨er hot zikh gegebn a shtel op⟩ in Voronezh

00:08:29.852 --> 00:08:34.504
un m'iz aropgeshprungen fun der ban. dos ershte geven, m'hot zikh aruntergeshtelt untern tender

00:08:35.099 --> 00:08:36.376
vos geyt UNK

00:08:36.685 --> 00:08:39.059
zikh opgegosn fun oybn biz arop

00:08:41.157 --> 00:08:43.956
un getrunken. dos tender vaser darf men nisht trinken.

00:08:43.956 --> 00:08:44.673
ober

00:08:44.685 --> 00:08:46.181
yene tsayt iz

00:08:46.322 --> 00:08:49.995
az s'iz nor geven vaser, zol zayn fun tender, zol zayn fun ⟨vos es⟩ zol nisht zayn.

00:08:51.958 --> 00:08:53.634
⟨ikh bin⟩ ongekumen keyn KUIBYSHEV.

00:08:53.662 --> 00:08:55.777
in KUIBYSHEV iz shoyn ariber geven

00:08:55.822 --> 00:08:57.639
NO, shpeter, di

00:08:58.286 --> 00:09:01.976
di sovyetishe regirung. KUIBYSHEV vert di tsaytvaylike hoyptshtot

00:09:02.218 --> 00:09:03.413
fun ratn farband

00:09:03.413 --> 00:09:05.739
un di regirung, ale regirungs amtn

00:09:05.880 --> 00:09:07.680
fun Moskve forn ariber

00:09:08.006 --> 00:09:09.114
keyn KUIBYSHEV.

00:09:10.723 --> 00:09:15.015
in KUIBYSHEV tsuzamengetrofn mit nokh pleytim, UNK zey hot men shoyn bashtimt

00:09:15.015 --> 00:09:16.793
tsu forn in a kolkhoz.

00:09:17.709 --> 00:09:20.538
s'iz geven a sakh yidn tsvishn zey?

00:09:19.582 --> 00:09:20.555
yo!

00:09:21.540 --> 00:09:24.420
alts fun, fun Poyln?

00:09:22.890 --> 00:09:24.178
alts fun

00:09:24.178 --> 00:09:27.258
Poyln, fun mayrev Ukrayne, Poyln

00:09:27.258 --> 00:09:30.546
UNK mayrev Ukrayne un Poyln s'iz geven di zelbe geshikhte.

00:09:32.998 --> 00:09:36.587
⟨nu, zog ikh⟩ vos hob ikh do tsu farlirn, zey forn in kolkhoz

00:09:36.778 --> 00:09:39.641
vel ikh mikh tsutshepn zikh tsu zey. s'iz geven efsher a grupe

00:09:40.608 --> 00:09:41.969
fun fuftsn man

00:09:42.785 --> 00:09:45.834
alts yugntlekhe, nisht keyn geheyrate f-.

00:09:48.388 --> 00:09:49.732
un oyf aza oyfn

00:09:50.295 --> 00:09:52.584
kum ikh on in kolkhoz oyfn dorf.

00:09:54.210 --> 00:09:56.381
m'hot zikh ⟨dermit⟩ zeyer shtark derfreyt

00:09:57.028 --> 00:09:59.520
az s'iz punkt geven in same shnit.

00:10:00.808 --> 00:10:03.756
m'hot UNK gedarft aropnemen dos geretenish fun feld

00:10:04.790 --> 00:10:06.154
un

00:10:06.174 --> 00:10:08.835
vi gezogt, ⟨frier⟩ far arbet hob ikh nisht moyre gehat.

00:10:10.140 --> 00:10:13.256
tsugevoynt tsu arbet un tsu noyt iz men geven tsugevoynt.

00:10:14.426 --> 00:10:16.361
mikh ayngelebt in dem dorf

00:10:18.999 --> 00:10:23.077
iz vider di zelbe geshikhte. di daytshn hobn zikh d- tsugerukt biz Stalingrad.

00:10:24.517 --> 00:10:27.194
Stalingrad iz ⟨geven⟩ di tsveyte zayt Volge.

00:10:28.972 --> 00:10:31.737
iz di greste teyl hot ongehoybn vider tsu loyfn

00:10:31.773 --> 00:10:34.282
vayter tif, iz geven der kholem

00:10:34.929 --> 00:10:36.155
mitl Azye.

00:10:36.887 --> 00:10:42.113
mitl Azye, nokh dertsu dos barimte, dos barimte ort Tashkent

00:10:42.422 --> 00:10:46.365
vos s'iz do a zeyer interesant bukh, "Tashkent, di shtot fun broyt."

00:10:48.007 --> 00:10:49.520
ikh hob bashlosn ⟨bay zikh azoy⟩.

00:10:49.931 --> 00:10:52.254
ikh for nisht in ergets mer vayter.

00:10:53.053 --> 00:10:54.282
az tsu loyfn

00:10:54.282 --> 00:10:55.438
eyner aleyn

00:10:55.438 --> 00:10:56.743
hob ikh shtendik tsayt.

00:10:58.132 --> 00:11:00.472
bin ikh geblibn der eyntsiker yid in dem dorf.

00:11:01.237 --> 00:11:03.931
afile di ukraynishe-rusishe

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:06.517
⟨vos zey⟩ hobn zikh oykhet gehat UNK evakuirt

00:11:06.517 --> 00:11:10.007
zenen ongekumen in dem dorf, zenen oykhet avek tifer keyn Rusland.

00:11:11.666 --> 00:11:13.044
vos hob ikh tsu loyfn?

00:11:13.809 --> 00:11:15.575
ikh blayb in dem dorf.

00:11:17.505 --> 00:11:21.009
un az s'hot zikh ongehoybn ⟨tsutsurukn⟩ der daytshisher front tsu di Volge

00:11:21.639 --> 00:11:24.620
hot men undz organizirt, s'heyst alts frayvilik.

00:11:26.128 --> 00:11:28.656
bashtimt fun kolkhoz a gantse grupe

00:11:28.656 --> 00:11:29.632
yugnt

00:11:30.465 --> 00:11:31.928
tsu forn kopen

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:33.969
okopes kegn tanken

00:11:35.662 --> 00:11:38.998
lengoys di Volge, lengoys a gevisn opshnit fun di Volge.

00:11:43.863 --> 00:11:46.372
dort, bin ikh krank gevorn

00:11:47.947 --> 00:11:51.536
ikh bin farhaltn iber vinter ⟨hot men⟩ farhaltn in shpitol

00:11:51.592 --> 00:11:53.088
nor di geshikhte iz

00:11:54.056 --> 00:11:55.451
ven ikh bin geganen

00:11:56.300 --> 00:12:00.007
in shpitol arayn, zikh oyfgehoybn a ge- a shtarke shney shturem

00:12:03.708 --> 00:12:04.917
mh

00:12:05.160 --> 00:12:07.399
un ikh bavayz ontsukumen in shpitol arayn

00:12:08.163 --> 00:12:13.102
di gantse grupe, bin ikh geven aynge- ayngelebt shoyn mit di, mit di dorfishe yugnt

00:12:13.496 --> 00:12:17.743
az zey hobn geendikt di okopes un tsurikforn in kolkhoz arayn, ⟨zey hobn mikh⟩ arumgezukht

00:12:18.305 --> 00:12:20.662
⟨hot men nokh⟩ nisht gefinen keyn shum shpitol

