un bay di nakht az me geyt aheym, brengt zi tsurik di beheymes, zol avade a liter ondertha-

00:24:20.657 --> 00:24:21.596
yednfals

00:24:23.559 --> 00:24:25.106
s'iz adurkh der zumer

00:24:25.280 --> 00:24:27.181
un me ruft mikh in militer arayn.

00:24:29.077 --> 00:24:30.405
az me ruft, geyt men.

00:24:32.435 --> 00:24:37.762
kum in militer, oyf dem zamlpunkt, vu me ruft ale rekrutn in KUIBYSHEV

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:40.529
iz dos alts geven in di KUIBYSHEVer gegnt.

00:24:42.324 --> 00:24:47.313
un denstmol zikh UNK tsu shafn di natsyonale armeyen. di natsyonale armeyen vil zogn azoy.

00:24:48.078 --> 00:24:51.194
 natsyonale brigades un natsyonale armeyen.

00:24:51.555 --> 00:24:53.389
shaft zikh di poylishe armey.

00:24:54.643 --> 00:25:01.371
shaft zikh di tshekhishe opteylung un litvishe, un azoy fun ale natsyonalitetn vos zeyere gebitn zenen okupirt

00:25:01.967 --> 00:25:03.109
fun Daytshl-

00:25:03.232 --> 00:25:05.033
keyn yidishe iz nisht geven.

00:25:04.481 --> 00:25:05.319
neyn.

00:25:06.540 --> 00:25:09.977
dos ⟨vil ikh zogn⟩ vegn yidishe, di geshikhte fun natsyonalitet

00:25:10.370 --> 00:25:13.081
iz ⟨far⟩ a sakh iz azoy farplontert

00:25:13.391 --> 00:25:15.073
az zey kenen nisht farshteyn

00:25:15.264 --> 00:25:17.590
az me ken hobn a natsyonalitet

00:25:17.627 --> 00:25:18.999
un birgershaft.

00:25:18.999 --> 00:25:21.185
in Poyln un Rusland iz geven

00:25:21.204 --> 00:25:24.675
natsyonalitetn vos iz geganen loytn blut, loytn opshtam

00:25:24.765 --> 00:25:26.666
un zayn a birger fun land.

00:25:26.773 --> 00:25:28.691
dos iz nisht geven eyns mitn tsvey.

00:25:29.321 --> 00:25:32.229
ikh in ale mayne dokumentn UNK ongegebn alts EVREI.

00:25:32.229 --> 00:25:33.112
a yid.

00:25:33.658 --> 00:25:35.208
mayn natsyonalitet iz geven

00:25:35.210 --> 00:25:35.981
a yid.

00:25:36.695 --> 00:25:38.191
ober s'iz geven a sakh

00:25:38.838 --> 00:25:41.515
yidn vos zey hobn ongegebn zeyer natsyonalitet polyak.

00:25:42.348 --> 00:25:45.211
dos UNK geven der kamf nokh fun farn krig in Poyln.

00:25:46.449 --> 00:25:48.013
⟨aklal⟩ me ruft oys

00:25:49.554 --> 00:25:51.337
a grupe yidishe nemen

00:25:51.883 --> 00:25:53.222
in di poylishe armey.

00:25:53.222 --> 00:25:55.120
ruft oys a tsveyte grupe

00:25:55.140 --> 00:25:57.497
mit yidishe nemen, ikh tsvishn zey

00:25:58.008 --> 00:25:59.457
in di arbets armey.

00:25:59.457 --> 00:26:01.782
UNK arbets armey ken ⟨ikh⟩ shoyn.

00:26:02.193 --> 00:26:05.987
geganen in der ⟨sal⟩, UNK natshalnik fun UNK, fun zamlpunkt

00:26:05.987 --> 00:26:07.571
"vos kumt do for?"

00:26:08.893 --> 00:26:10.727
zogt er "vos vilstu fun mir?

00:26:12.082 --> 00:26:16.768
du in dayne papirn, host ongeshribn, host ongeshribn natsyonalitet EVREI?" "yo."

00:26:17.043 --> 00:26:18.759
"bistu dokh nisht keyn polyak?"

00:26:19.389 --> 00:26:22.809
zog ikh "ikh bin UNK geven a poylisher birger. ikh bin ⟨geboyrn⟩ in Varshe."

00:26:23.034 --> 00:26:25.239
"dos" zogt er "interesirt mikh nisht."

00:26:25.397 --> 00:26:26.961
bafel ⟨iz⟩ bafel.

00:26:27.152 --> 00:26:29.188
di UNK iz geven azoy groys

00:26:30.476 --> 00:26:33.646
me heyst shikn polyakn, shikt er polyakn. me heyst shikn yidn

00:26:33.665 --> 00:26:36.545
yidn nisht, shikt er UNK.

00:26:37.142 --> 00:26:42.165
dos hob ikh shoyn gehat mer ⟨mazl⟩. gekumen in di arbets armey, ⟨oykh⟩ vider genumen di fis oyf di pleytse.

00:26:42.626 --> 00:26:44.353
bald UNK ⟨farn⟩ tog

00:26:44.398 --> 00:26:47.059
un tsurik arop keyn KUIBYSHEV

00:26:48.971 --> 00:26:51.395
hob ikh gezen az do

00:26:52.160 --> 00:26:55.006
UNK khapn, iz a, iz an umglik.

00:26:55.063 --> 00:26:58.280
iz di ershte zakh, me git eynem a ⟨klep tsu⟩ iz ⟨dezertirer⟩.

00:27:00.767 --> 00:27:06.330
nisht lang getrakht, UNK zikh nokh aza khevreman vi ikh, a let, ⟨fun⟩ Letland

00:27:06.690 --> 00:27:07.798
zog ikh "her azoy.

00:27:08.968 --> 00:27:12.709
vet nemen tsvey broyt. du a broyt untern hant un ikh a broyt untern hant

00:27:12.849 --> 00:27:14.424
un m'vet zikh tsushteln

00:27:14.452 --> 00:27:16.610
tsum militerishn komandant fun di shtot

00:27:16.610 --> 00:27:18.953
in di militerishe komandatur fun di shtot.

00:27:20.595 --> 00:27:22.819
ikh vel zogn 'ikh heys azoy un azoy.

00:27:22.819 --> 00:27:27.980
ikh bin aropgeshprungen fun eshalon koyfn a broyt. bin tsurikgekumen oyf di stantsye

00:27:28.779 --> 00:27:31.558
iz di ban avek. me vet dokh nisht vartn oyf mir.'"

00:27:32.238 --> 00:27:33.245
UNK

00:27:33.977 --> 00:27:37.043
ahin, aher, kum tsu UNK militerishe komandatur

00:27:37.149 --> 00:27:39.438
"oy, ikh azelkh, azelkh, azel-

00:27:39.917 --> 00:27:40.749
UNK."

00:27:40.749 --> 00:27:43.609
oysgezen yung, a bisl tsugeveynt, a bisl dos

00:27:43.609 --> 00:27:47.049
UNK vos bin ikh shuldik? UNK gekoyfn a broyt, iz di ban avekgeforn.

00:27:47.308 --> 00:27:53.141
UNK di gantse militerishe komandant fun di stantsye. zog ikh "der komandant hot mikh geshikt tsu dir."

00:27:55.695 --> 00:27:56.398
ah!

00:27:56.893 --> 00:27:58.541
nokh a tsvey dray sho

00:27:58.749 --> 00:28:01.916
ophaltn, ruft er mikh aroys. "vi azoy heystu?"

00:28:02.748 --> 00:28:04.340
nu, hob ikh shoyn getoysht

00:28:04.352 --> 00:28:05.393
dem nomen.

00:28:07.119 --> 00:28:14.592
fun Fayvl gevorn FRANTSISKO. fun Zilberberg iz gevorn Svirovski, far di mayn- di eltern mayne, di mame

00:28:14.628 --> 00:28:16.681
in der heym hot geheysn Svirovski

00:28:18.155 --> 00:28:26.621
far UNK dray yor UNK mayn yor tsvey un tsvontsik volt der kheshbn nisht geshtimt, far di tsvey un tsvantsikster yorgang iz shoyn geven

00:28:26.829 --> 00:28:28.680
halb tseshosn, halb

00:28:29.057 --> 00:28:30.536
toyt oyfn front

00:28:31.740 --> 00:28:34.266
geboyrn in Varshe, ⟨altsding⟩ fayn un gut, UNK.

00:28:34.912 --> 00:28:37.016
me geyt mikh ⟨UNK⟩shraybn UNK

00:28:38.490 --> 00:28:40.867
di bashtetikung, un shikt mikh tsurik

00:28:40.867 --> 00:28:43.226
oyfn zamlpunkt. fun dem zamlpunkt

00:28:43.350 --> 00:28:46.568
bin ikh shoyn geforn direkt arayn in di poylishe armey.
